			<div class="comment-content"><p>Hi</p>
<p>Just a quick question but why the 1632c chip spec and not the 1632? What is the difference please?<br />
Mark</p>
</div>

			<div class="reply">
				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/about/?replytocom=21#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-21", "21", "respond", "2")'>Reply <span>&darr;</span></a>			</div><!-- .reply -->
