									</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->

				
			</footer>

			<div class="comment-content"><p>Nick, Many thanks for the clock design.  After waiting for a couple of weeks for the LEDs to arrive from Hong Kong I now have a red version up and running. <a href="http://youtu.be/t0pA_k7Px80" rel="nofollow">http://youtu.be/t0pA_k7Px80</a><br />
I did spot one thing on the circuit layout diagram which seems to differ from your photographs.  The connections to the DS1307 seem to be the wrong way around.  Using your numbering I have:<br />
pin 5 to +5V<br />
pin 6 unconnected<br />
pin 7 to Arduino A5<br />
pin 8 to Arduino A4</p>
<p>Many thanks again.</p>
</div>

