			<div class="comment-content"><p>Yes that should work unless you have a short. Both the LED boards and the arduino need 5 volts, so it&#8217;s just a case of connecting them together. Have you got a circuit tester &#8211; maybe test to see what happens to the voltage when you connect the LED&#8217;s.</p>
<p>Nick</p>
</div>

