			<footer class="comment-meta">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
					<img alt='' src='http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/bf8dc7ec2876168709cd70a41ae19d8b?s=68&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G' class='avatar avatar-68' height='68' width='68' /><span class="fn"><a href='http://timewitharduino.blogspot.com/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>FlorinC</a></span> on <a href="http://123led.wordpress.com/about/#comment-278"><time datetime="2011-06-28T21:47:50+00:00">June 28, 2011 at 21:47</time></a> <span class="says">said:</span>
									</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->

				
