			<div class="comment-content"><p>Not sure if this helps, but I found this in function ht1632_setup() in my code:</p>
<p>#ifdef _16x24_<br />
  ht1632_sendcmd(HT1632_CMD_COMS11);  // 16*32, PMOS drivers<br />
#else<br />
// (fc)<br />
  ht1632_sendcmd(HT1632_CMD_COMS10);  // 32&#215;8, PMOS drivers<br />
#endif</p>
<p>Basically, you send the first command for the 16&#215;24 display and the second for the 0832 display.</p>
</div>

