	<li class="comment byuser comment-author-123led bypostauthor odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1 highlander-comment" id="li-comment-281">
		<article id="comment-281" class="comment">
			<footer class="comment-meta">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
					<img alt='' src='http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/86b77e4f66a277fad74763ee5dcdb2d4?s=68&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G' class='avatar avatar-68' height='68' width='68' /><span class="fn">Nick</span> on <a href="http://123led.wordpress.com/about/#comment-281"><time datetime="2011-06-29T20:32:32+00:00">June 29, 2011 at 20:32</time></a> <span class="says">said:</span>
