									</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->

				
			</footer>

			<div class="comment-content"><p>Hey Poto. If you leave it in pong mode, does the time freeze or the ball too?</p>
<p>If it&#8217;s the time, I woud check the wiring to the clock chip &#8211; power data etc.</p>
<p>If it&#8217;s the whole thing check the wiring to the arduino and make sure you power supply is good, If it wavers it could cause things to lock up.</p>
<p>Nick</p>
</div>

