			<div class="comment-content"><p>What a great looking project. I have ordered the display&#8217;s and wired it up and I can get the left part of the display working on both halves of the display by changing the switches but can&#8217;t get the whole display to work. I did see it operate once but the R an L was switched around. I turned it OFF then ON again and since I have just had a one sided display. I am thinking maybe a reset pulse but thought maybe you have saw this before.</p>
</div>

			<div class="reply">
				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/about/?replytocom=5366#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-5366", "5366", "respond", "2")'>Reply <span>&darr;</span></a>			</div><!-- .reply -->
