			<footer class="comment-meta">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
					<img alt='' src='http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/86b77e4f66a277fad74763ee5dcdb2d4?s=39&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G' class='avatar avatar-39' height='39' width='39' /><span class="fn">Nick</span> on <a href="http://123led.wordpress.com/about/#comment-9859"><time datetime="2012-10-12T22:38:46+00:00">October 12, 2012 at 22:38</time></a> <span class="says">said:</span>
