			<div class="comment-content"><p>Oh just to update, I did google on the pin configuration and got it working correctly. One of the way of knowing is that when you have wiring wrong on the chip you only get the pong clock version 4.0 and nothing moves further. Once you fix your wiring on the chip every thing works except time is not correct.</p>
