			<div class="comment-content"><p>Hi Nick, I see you are looking to get a PCB designed ? I would give it a go, however I feel you would be better to design a PCB shield for the UNO. If you want a complete PCB so you can do away with the Uno, you will need to replicate what Arduino have done so fantasticlly and people would need to have the Atmel with the boot loader already burnt, and you would still need to provide a way of uploading the code. Let me know if you want me to have a crack at it.</p>
