	<li class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1 highlander-comment" id="li-comment-24368">
		<article id="comment-24368" class="comment">
			<footer class="comment-meta">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
					<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/6e938d516ca8527b0038d786af8b43c7?s=68&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G' class='avatar avatar-68' height='68' width='68' /><span class="fn">jesper</span> on <a href="http://123led.wordpress.com/about/#comment-24368"><time datetime="2014-03-18T14:10:28+00:00">March 18, 2014 at 14:10</time></a> <span class="says">said:</span>
